text: Robert Carter-Shaw (born 21 November 1941) is an English cricketer. He played one first-class match for Cambridge University Cricket Club in 1962. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:People from Berkhamsted
